itunes:title: MAR 09 2022 - WAR IN UKRAINE - DAY 14 UPDATE
title: MAR 09 2022 - WAR IN UKRAINE - DAY 14 UPDATE
description:
The Institute for the Study of War is reporting that Russian forces continue to concentrate in the outskirts of Kyiv for a planned assault on the capital in the coming 24-96 hours. Meanwhile, Victoria Nuland, the Under Secretary of State for Political Affairs of the US testifies in Congress revealing that the United States has been working alongside Ukraine to prevent biolab research facilities from falling into Russian hands. All of this as the Russian invasion of Ukraine impacts increasing costs of agricultural goods, and Project Veritas exposes New York Times journalist, Matthew Rosenberg who claims January 6th media coverage was an “overreaction,” the FBI was involved, and despite ongoing narrative, was “not organized.”


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
